OL,4,G0100FThe Yorkshire Vet
OL,5,     GRottweiler cross Adol could maybe
OL,6,     Ghave a career as a sniffer dog -
OL,7,     Ghe's found what seems to be bag
OL,8,     Gof Class A drugs. But his owner
OL,9,     GMatthew is worried that Adol's
OL,10,     Geaten a second bag.
OL,11,G0200FCruising with Jane McDonald
OL,12,     GJane's trip starts in The
OL,13,     GEverglades or sea of grass as the
OL,14,     Glocals call it. Covering one
OL,15,     Gpoint five million acres, this
OL,16,     Gwetland is half the size of
OL,17,     GYorkshire.
